## Your manufacturing   partner for mobility

[Products![](https://www.tekniagroup.com/wp-content/themes/Teknia/img/arrows/arrow-button.svg)](https://www.tekniagroup.com/en/solutions/products/) [Technologies![](https://www.tekniagroup.com/wp-content/themes/Teknia/img/arrows/arrow-button.svg)](https://www.tekniagroup.com/en/solutions/our-technologies/)

###### Who we are

### About Teknia

Teknia is a multinational group specialized in the manufacture of metal and plastic components for mobility solutions using a wide range of technologies.

![](https://www.tekniagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/fabrica-de-bilbao-teknia.jpg)

![](https://www.tekniagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/teknia-countries.jpg)

![](https://www.tekniagroup.com/wp-content/themes/Teknia/img/icons/square.png)

Teknia is a global, multi-technology partner for leading manufacturers in the automotive industry. Its technologies are machining, stamping, tube forming, plastic injection and aluminium injection or High Pressure Die Casting (HPDC).

[Know us![](https://www.tekniagroup.com/wp-content/themes/Teknia/img/arrows/arrow-button.svg)](https://www.tekniagroup.com/en/who-we-are/)

![](https://www.tekniagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/teknia-plants.jpg)

###### PEOPLE

##### Teknia is built part by part

Teknia is the sum of its factories and the people who form part of its team. A group where diversity is the protagonist and where people from different generations work together to keep improving every day.

[Discover the #PartByPart campaign![](https://www.tekniagroup.com/wp-content/themes/Teknia/img/arrows/arrow-button.svg)](https://www.tekniagroup.com/en/who-we-are/people/generational-change/)

![Sustainability](https://www.tekniagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/memoria-image-1.png)

###### memoria

### Sustainability Report 2023

Sustainability is integrated into Teknia’s business strategy and is part of the day-to-day work of the company’s people and operations.

[2023 Report![](https://www.tekniagroup.com/wp-content/themes/Teknia/img/arrows/arrow-button.svg)](https://www.tekniagroup.com/en/who-we-are/sustainability-report/)

###### Sustainability

##### Towards the mobility of the future

The spirit of Teknia, since its foundation, has been based on making a positive environmental and social contribution to the territories where the company operates.

[Know more![](https://www.tekniagroup.com/wp-content/themes/Teknia/img/arrows/arrow-button.svg)](https://www.tekniagroup.com/en/who-we-are/commitments/sustainability/)
